Following demand online, I've uploaded assembled grand cruisers for each of:
- Vengeance
- Exorcist
- Goliath
- Avenger
- Annihilator
- Vindictive
- "Iron Wolf" Vindictive

Some slight changes but these are basically the combination of other peoples work - I cant take credit for these great designs! The repulsive is by Chios, the basic grand cruisers from Italian Moose, and alternative parts made by tinnut and mmoresco35. Please check these guys out; they have great stuff!
